task: Create a new contact for Sophie dos Santos. Their number is +18210700009. (name: Sophie dos Santos, phone: +18210700009)

action.description: Tap the Phone app icon to open it and access the contacts functionality.
Tap the "Contacts" tab in the bottom navigation bar to access the contacts list.
Tap the "Create new contact" option to start adding a new contact.
Tap the "First name" field to begin entering the contact's first name.
Type "Sophie" into the First name field.
Tap the "Last name" field to begin entering the last name.
Type "dos Santos" into the Last name field.
Tap the "Phone" field to begin entering the phone number.
Type "+18210700009" into the Phone field.
Tap the "Save" button to save the new contact.
